{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This session is being continued from a previous conversation that ran out of context. The conversation is summarized below:\nAnalysis:\nLet me chronologically analyze the conversation:\n\n1. **User's Initial Request**: The user provided a comprehensive migration checklist to migrate a Java PetClinic application from Quarkus to Spring Boot. This is an autonomous one-shot migration with specific requirements around Docker isolation, testing, and documentation.\n\n2. **Codebase Analysis Phase**: \n   - Explored the directory structure at `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__quarkus__spring/run_2/output/`\n   - Read all Java source files (27 files), HTML templates (10 files), configuration files, SQL scripts\n   - The app is a Quarkus 3.30.5 PetClinic using JAX-RS, Qute templates, Hibernate Panache, H2/PostgreSQL\n\n3. **Migration Work Completed**:\n   - Created new pom.xml with Spring Boot 3.2.5 dependencies\n   - Created smoke.py test file\n   - Created all new Spring Boot Java classes (entities, repositories, controllers)\n   - Converted all Qute templates to Thymeleaf templates\n   - Updated application.properties for Spring Boot\n   - Created data.sql from import.sql\n   - Moved static resources to Spring Boot locations\n   - Created compiled CSS from SCSS sources\n   - Updated Dockerfile for Spring Boot\n   - Removed old Quarkus source files\n   - Built Docker image successfully\n   - Started container and verified it's running (port 33870)\n   - Did a quick curl test showing 200 on home page\n\n4. **Errors encountered**:\n   - Write tool errors: \"File has not been read yet\" - needed to re-read files before overwriting\n   - Docker env variable issues: `$SCARF_IMAGE_TAG` wasn't expanding properly in Bash tool - used hardcoded tag `scarf_petclinic_spring:latest` instead\n   - Bash `$()` command substitution syntax error - the tool was escaping parentheses\n\n5. **Current state**: \n   - Docker image built and running on port 33870\n   - Home page returns 200\n   - Smoke tests haven't been run yet\n   - CHANGELOG.md hasn't been created yet\n   - The todo list shows smoke tests and CHANGELOG.md as pending\n\n6. **Last action before summary**: Quick curl test to http://localhost:33870/ returning 200 status code\n\nSummary:\n1. Primary Request and Intent:\n   The user requested a complete autonomous migration of a Java PetClinic application from Quarkus 3.30.5 to Spring Boot, following a detailed migration checklist. Key requirements include:\n   - Analyze the existing codebase\n   - Generate smoke tests (smoke.py)\n   - Update pom.xml, configuration, Dockerfile\n   - Refactor all Java code from Quarkus APIs to Spring Boot APIs\n   - Migrate Qute templates to Thymeleaf\n   - Build as Docker image, run container, execute smoke tests\n   - Document everything in CHANGELOG.md\n   - Docker isolation: use `$SCARF_CONTAINER_NAME`, `$SCARF_IMAGE_TAG`, and dynamic port allocation `-p 0:8080`\n\n2. Key Technical Concepts:\n   - **Quarkus → Spring Boot 3.2.5** framework migration\n   - **JAX-RS** (`@Path`, `@GET`, `@POST`, `@Produces`) → **Spring MVC** (`@Controller`, `@GetMapping`, `@PostMapping`)\n   - **Hibernate Panache** (`PanacheEntity`, static methods like `listAll()`, `findById()`, `persist()`) → **Spring Data JPA** (`JpaRepository` interfaces)\n   - **Qute templates** (`{#include base}`, `{#for}`, `{msg:xxx}`, `{#if}`) → **Thymeleaf** (`th:replace`, `th:each`, `th:text`, `th:if`)\n   - **CDI** (`@Inject`, `@ApplicationScoped`) → **Spring DI** (constructor injection, `@Controller`)\n   - **Quarkus i18n** (`@MessageBundle`, `@Localized`) → Hardcoded English strings (simplified)\n   - **JAX-RS `@BeanParam`/`@FormParam`** → Spring MVC `@RequestParam` and `@Valid` with `BindingResult`\n   - **Panache entity pattern** (public fields, static query methods) → **JPA entities with getters/setters** + repository pattern\n   - H2 in-memory database for dev, PostgreSQL for prod\n   - Docker containerization with Maven build\n\n3. Files and Code Sections:\n\n   **Original Quarkus Files Read (all removed after migration):**\n   - `src/main/java/org/quarkus/samples/petclinic/JaxRsApplication.java` - JAX-RS Application class with `@Blocking`\n   - `src/main/java/org/quarkus/samples/petclinic/Temporals.java` - Qute `@TemplateExtension` for date formatting\n   - `src/main/java/org/quarkus/samples/petclinic/model/Person.java` - Base entity extending `PanacheEntity` with public fields and `@FormParam`\n   - `src/main/java/org/quarkus/samples/petclinic/owner/Owner.java` - Owner entity with `PanacheEntity`, static `findByLastName()`, `attach()` methods\n   - `src/main/java/org/quarkus/samples/petclinic/owner/Pet.java` - Pet entity with `PanacheEntity`\n   - `src/main/java/org/quarkus/samples/petclinic/owner/PetType.java` - PetType with `@TemplateExtension` Formatter class\n   - `src/main/java/org/quarkus/samples/petclinic/owner/OwnerForm.java` - Form DTO with `@FormParam`\n   - `src/main/java/org/quarkus/samples/petclinic/owner/OwnersResource.java` - JAX-RS resource returning `TemplateInstance`\n   - `src/main/java/org/quarkus/samples/petclinic/owner/PetResource.java` - JAX-RS pet resource\n   - `src/main/java/org/quarkus/samples/petclinic/owner/VisitResource.java` - JAX-RS visit resource\n   - `src/main/java/org/quarkus/samples/petclinic/owner/VisitComparator.java` - Comparator for visits\n   - `src/main/java/org/quarkus/samples/petclinic/owner/LocalDateConverter.java` - JAX-RS ParamConverter\n   - `src/main/java/org/quarkus/samples/petclinic/owner/LocalDateParamConverterProvider.java` - JAX-RS provider\n   - `src/main/java/org/quarkus/samples/petclinic/visit/Visit.java` - Visit entity with Panache\n   - `src/main/java/org/quarkus/samples/petclinic/vet/Vet.java` - Vet entity\n   - `src/main/java/org/quarkus/samples/petclinic/vet/Vets.java` - Vets wrapper DTO\n   - `src/main/java/org/quarkus/samples/petclinic/vet/VetResource.java` - JAX-RS vet resource\n   - `src/main/java/org/quarkus/samples/petclinic/vet/Specialty.java` - Specialty entity\n   - `src/main/java/org/quarkus/samples/petclinic/vet/SpecialityComparator.java`\n   - `src/main/java/org/quarkus/samples/petclinic/system/WelcomeResource.java` - JAX-RS welcome\n   - `src/main/java/org/quarkus/samples/petclinic/system/Templates.java` - Qute `@CheckedTemplate` with native methods\n   - `src/main/java/org/quarkus/samples/petclinic/system/TemplatesLocale.java` - Locale-aware template wrapper\n   - `src/main/java/org/quarkus/samples/petclinic/system/CrashResource.java` - Error trigger\n   - `src/main/java/org/quarkus/samples/petclinic/system/ErrorExceptionMapper.java` - JAX-RS `@ServerExceptionMapper`\n   - `src/main/java/org/quarkus/samples/petclinic/system/AppMessages.java` - `@MessageBundle` i18n interface\n   - `src/main/java/org/quarkus/samples/petclinic/system/SpanishAppMessages.java` - Spanish translations\n   - `src/main/java/org/quarkus/samples/petclinic/system/LocaleVariantCreator.java`\n   - 10 Qute HTML templates (base.html, welcome.html, error.html, vetList.html, findOwners.html, ownersList.html, ownerDetails.html, createOrUpdateOwnerForm.html, createOrUpdatePetForm.html, createOrUpdateVisitForm.html)\n   - `src/main/resources/application.properties` - Quarkus profile-specific config\n   - `src/main/resources/import.sql` - Seed data\n   - 4 SCSS files (petclinic.scss, header.scss, typography.scss, responsive.scss)\n\n   **New Spring Boot Files Created:**\n\n   - `pom.xml` - Replaced Quarkus BOM and plugins with Spring Boot parent 3.2.5, spring-boot-starter-web, spring-boot-starter-thymeleaf, spring-boot-starter-data-jpa, spring-boot-starter-validation, H2, PostgreSQL, webjars, webjars-locator-core, jackson-databind, spring-boot-starter-test\n   \n   - `src/main/java/org/springframework/samples/petclinic/PetClinicApplication.java` - Main Spring Boot application class:\n     ```java\n     @SpringBootApplication\n     public class PetClinicApplication {\n         public static void main(String[] args) {\n             SpringApplication.run(PetClinicApplication.class, args);\n         }\n     }\n     ```\n\n   - `src/main/java/org/springframework/samples/petclinic/model/Person.java` - Base entity with `@MappedSuperclass`, `@Id`, `@GeneratedValue`, private fields with getters/setters (removed PanacheEntity, @FormParam)\n\n   - `src/main/java/org/springframework/samples/petclinic/owner/Owner.java` - Owner entity extending Person with `@JsonManagedReference` on pets, standard JPA with getters/setters\n\n   - `src/main/java/org/springframework/samples/petclinic/owner/Pet.java` - Pet entity with standard JPA, `@JsonBackReference` on owner, `@Transient` visits, `getSortedVisits()` method\n\n   - `src/main/java/org/springframework/samples/petclinic/owner/PetType.java` - PetType entity with standard JPA\n\n   - `src/main/java/org/springframework/samples/petclinic/visit/Visit.java` - Visit entity with standard JPA\n\n   - `src/main/java/org/springframework/samples/petclinic/vet/Specialty.java` - Specialty entity\n   - `src/main/java/org/springframework/samples/petclinic/vet/Vet.java` - Vet entity with `getSpecialties()` returning sorted list, `getNrOfSpecialties()`\n   - `src/main/java/org/springframework/samples/petclinic/vet/Vets.java` - DTO wrapper\n\n   - `src/main/java/org/springframework/samples/petclinic/owner/OwnerRepository.java`:\n     ```java\n     @Repository\n     public interface OwnerRepository extends JpaRepository<Owner, Long> {\n         Collection<Owner> findByLastName(String lastName);\n     }\n     ```\n\n   - `src/main/java/org/springframework/samples/petclinic/owner/PetRepository.java` - JpaRepository<Pet, Long>\n   - `src/main/java/org/springframework/samples/petclinic/owner/PetTypeRepository.java` - JpaRepository with `findByName(String name)`\n   - `src/main/java/org/springframework/samples/petclinic/visit/VisitRepository.java` - JpaRepository with `findByPetId(Long petId)`\n   - `src/main/java/org/springframework/samples/petclinic/vet/VetRepository.java` - JpaRepository<Vet, Long>\n\n   - `src/main/java/org/springframework/samples/petclinic/owner/OwnerController.java` - Spring MVC controller with constructor injection, `@GetMapping`/`@PostMapping` for all owner CRUD operations, `@Valid` with `BindingResult`, `@ResponseBody` for JSON API endpoint `/owners/api/list`\n\n   - `src/main/java/org/springframework/samples/petclinic/owner/PetController.java` - Spring MVC controller for pet CRUD, uses `@RequestParam` for form fields\n\n   - `src/main/java/org/springframework/samples/petclinic/owner/VisitController.java` - Spring MVC controller for visit creation\n\n   - `src/main/java/org/springframework/samples/petclinic/vet/VetController.java` - Spring MVC controller:\n     ```java\n     @GetMapping(\"/vets.html\")\n     public String showResourcesVetPage(Model model) { ... }\n     @GetMapping(\"/vets\")\n     @ResponseBody\n     public Vets showResourcesVetList() { ... }\n     ```\n\n   - `src/main/java/org/springframework/samples/petclinic/system/WelcomeController.java` - Returns \"welcome\" view\n   - `src/main/java/org/springframework/samples/petclinic/system/CrashController.java` - Throws RuntimeException at `/oups`\n   - `src/main/java/org/springframework/samples/petclinic/system/ErrorController.java` - `@ControllerAdvice` with `@ExceptionHandler(Exception.class)`\n\n   - `src/main/resources/templates/fragments/layout.html` - Thymeleaf layout fragment with `th:fragment=\"head\"`, `th:fragment=\"navbar\"`, `th:fragment=\"scripts\"`\n   - All 9 Thymeleaf templates converted from Qute syntax\n   - `src/main/resources/application.properties` - Spring Boot config with H2, JPA create-drop, data.sql loading\n   - `src/main/resources/data.sql` - Copied from import.sql (same seed data)\n   - `src/main/resources/static/css/petclinic.css` - Manually compiled from SCSS\n   - Static resources (imag